OBVIOUSLY NOT.

00:26.026 --> 00:27.594
BENJAMIN YOUNG,
YOU ARE UNDER ARREST

00:27.594 --> 00:28.995
FOR THE MURDER
OF QUINCY MAXWELL.

00:28.995 --> 00:30.731
BEHIND YOUR BACK.

00:30.731 --> 00:31.965
‐TAKE HIM IN.
‐HOLD UP, MAN.

00:31.965 --> 00:34.000
NO, THERE IS NO HOLD UP.
YOU DIDN'T WANT TO TALK TO US.

00:34.000 --> 00:35.201
