TAKE YOU IN FOR.

00:49.716 --> 00:51.384
NO, YOU CAN'T.
I'M NOT DOING NOTHING.

00:51.384 --> 00:54.788
I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.
YOU SURE?

00:54.788 --> 00:56.523
YEAH, I'M SURE.
