THE D. A. IS GOING TO SEE IT.

01:04.470 --> 01:07.307
COME ON, MAN. YOU GOT
TO HAVE PROBABLE CAUSE, AND...

01:07.307 --> 01:09.809
OH, WE DO.

01:09.809 --> 01:11.377
WAIT. WHAT THE HELL, MAN?
I DIDN'T DO NOTHING.

01:11.377 --> 01:13.413
OKAY?
NO, IT'S NOT OKAY.

01:13.413 --> 01:14.414
NOW, DO YOU WANT TO TALK
ABOUT THIS?

01:14.414 --> 01:15.616
