01:43.910 --> 01:46.012
OKAY.

01:46.012 --> 01:48.515
MITCH, DON'T SAY NOTHING
TO MY MAMA ABOUT THIS, PLEASE.

01:48.515 --> 01:50.116
DON'T WORRY.
ALL RIGHT? LOOK.

01:50.116 --> 01:51.117
I AIN'T GOING TO SAY NOTHING.
I'M GOING TO GET YOU A LAWYER.

01:51.117 --> 01:52.485
ALL RIGHT?
I'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

01:52.485 --> 01:53.920
