I'M GONNA HIT HER UP.

02:02.402 --> 02:03.870
WHO?

02:03.870 --> 02:05.138
VERONICA.
NO, DO NOT.

02:05.138 --> 02:06.339
DO NOT HIT HER UP.

02:06.339 --> 02:08.809
THAT'S YOUR ONLY CHANCE, MAN.

02:08.809 --> 02:11.578
DON'T.

02:11.578 --> 02:12.613
THERE SHE
IS RIGHT THERE.

02:12.613 --> 02:14.414
MRS. HARRINGTON!

02:14.414 --> 02:15.916
YES?

02:15.916 --> 02:17.383
