TO YOU, PLEASE?

02:17.383 --> 02:18.952
OH.

02:18.952 --> 02:21.154
‐WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?
‐HE'S BEEN ARRESTED.

02:21.154 --> 02:22.589
I SEE THAT.
