02:25.258 --> 02:26.993
NO, YOU CAN TALK
TO HIM DOWNTOWN.

02:26.993 --> 02:31.231
I AM HIS LAWYER.
I WILL TALK TO HIM RIGHT NOW.

02:31.231 --> 02:34.901
