MRS. HARRINGTON.

02:34.901 --> 02:36.803
‐MAN, COME ON.
‐BENJAMIN, DON'T SAY A WORD.

02:36.803 --> 02:39.405
I WILL BE THERE.
DON'T SAY ANYTHING.

02:39.405 --> 02:40.406
IT'S NOT RIGHT.

02:40.406 --> 02:43.143
NOT RIGHT,
MRS. HARRINGTON.

02:43.143 --> 02:45.879
WE'LL GET HIM OUT.

02:45.879 --> 02:46.947
