04:49.816 --> 04:52.553
ABOUT THAT GIRL
YOU'RE SEEING.

04:52.553 --> 04:54.655
WHERE DID YOU MEET HER,
DAVID?

04:54.655 --> 04:56.957
I DON'T KNOW
MELISSA'S LAST NAME.

04:56.957 --> 04:58.525
