05:39.873 --> 05:42.475
SO YOU'RE NOT GONNA
TELL ME WHERE JEFFERY IS.

05:46.012 --> 05:49.883
[ SIGHS ]
YOU KNOW THAT.

05:49.883 --> 05:54.788
AND YOU'RE NOT GONNA
TELL ME MELISSA'S LAST NAME.

05:54.788 --> 05:58.458
