IF YOU GIVE ME YOURS.

06:11.177 --> 06:14.515
♪♪♪♪

06:14.515 --> 06:16.583
NOW, WHERE DID YOU
MEET THIS GIRL?

06:18.919 --> 06:21.955
♪♪♪♪

06:23.890 --> 06:26.960
