06:26.960 --> 06:28.094
OKAY.

06:31.164 --> 06:36.269
I HOPE YOU ENJOY WAITING
BECAUSE...

06:36.269 --> 06:39.906
IT'LL PROBABLY
BE A WHILE.

06:39.906 --> 06:45.078
YOU PUSHED THAT GIRL INTO TRYING
TO TAKE HER OWN LIFE.

06:45.078 --> 06:47.748
I WOULD NEVER DO THAT.

06:47.748 --> 06:51.184
YOU JUST DON'T GET IT,
DO YOU,

06:51.184 --> 06:53.419
WHAT THE HELL YOU PUT
ONTO PEOPLE IS CAUSING.

06:53.419 --> 06:55.756
CAUSING?
WHAT?

06:58.625 --> 07:00.233
I'M GLAD I LEFT YOU.

07:03.136 --> 07:06.439
‐ARE YOU SURE YOU'RE GONE?
‐I COULDN'T BE MORE GONE.

07:10.010 --> 07:11.945
I'M GLAD YOU THINK SO.

07:11.945 --> 07:14.715
OH, I KNOW SO,
AND YOU NEED TO KNOW.

07:14.715 --> 07:18.218
♪♪♪♪

07:18.218 --> 07:22.155
STRANGE THING
ABOUT MARRIAGE.

07:22.155 --> 07:26.593
WHEN YOU LOVE SOMEONE,
YOU REALLY LOVE SOMEONE...

07:28.929 --> 07:32.933
