07:32.933 --> 07:35.401
NOT KNOWING THAT ONE DAY,

07:35.401 --> 07:39.806
ONE...MAD DAY WILL COME.

07:41.875 --> 07:44.845
AND WHEN THAT MAD DAY COMES,

07:44.845 --> 07:49.182
THAT VERY PERSON
THAT YOU LOVE SO MUCH...

07:52.185 --> 07:53.620
HAS YOUR DEEPEST,

07:53.620 --> 07:59.359
DARKEST SECRETS LOCKED AWAY.

07:59.359 --> 08:01.502
YOU DON'T SCARE ME.

08:01.502 --> 08:03.369
I KNOW.

08:03.369 --> 08:05.706
THAT'S WHAT EVERYONE SAYS.

08:05.706 --> 08:08.408
♪♪♪♪

08:08.408 --> 08:10.343
BUT WHAT I KNOW
SHOULD SCARE YOU.

08:10.343 --> 08:12.378
HMM.

08:12.378 --> 08:15.248
YOU THINK I DON'T
KNOW YOUR DIRT?

08:15.248 --> 08:16.817
HMM.

08:16.817 --> 08:20.286
