HOW CLEVER I AM.

08:20.286 --> 08:24.057
NO.

08:24.057 --> 08:26.527
I KNOW YOU ARE
LIKE A RABID WOLF.

08:26.527 --> 08:28.995
[ IMITATING DOG HOWLING ]

08:33.700 --> 08:36.469
LOOK AT THIS.

08:36.469 --> 08:37.904
VERONICA.

08:37.904 --> 08:39.305
BASTARD.

08:41.975 --> 08:45.646
YOU TWO LOOK...TENSE.

08:47.280 --> 08:49.983
WELL, YOU BRING THAT KIND
OF THING OUT OF US.

08:49.983 --> 08:53.486
HMM.

08:53.486 --> 08:56.122
YOU DOING GOOD, DAVID?

08:56.122 --> 08:58.759
YEAH.

08:58.759 --> 09:00.534
YOU GET THE NUMBER TRACED?

09:03.537 --> 09:05.572
HE'S WORKING ON IT.

09:05.572 --> 09:08.108
WELL, DAMN IT, DAVID.
HE BETTER WORK ON IT QUICK.

09:08.108 --> 09:11.244
OKAY?

09:11.244 --> 09:12.478
HE NEEDS TO HURRY IT UP.

09:12.478 --> 09:13.780
MM‐HMM.

09:13.780 --> 09:18.251
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU
TWO DEVILS DOING NOW?

09:18.251 --> 09:21.454
DEVILS?
REALLY?

09:21.454 --> 09:25.091
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT,
LEADER OF LEGION?

09:25.091 --> 09:26.326
YOU KNOW DAVID AND I,

09:26.326 --> 09:29.095
