CATS AS USUAL.

09:29.095 --> 09:31.497
OH, YOU'RE FOND OF CATS,
ARE YOU?

09:31.497 --> 09:35.569
YES, I AM, LOTS AND LOTS
AND LOTS OF CATS.

09:35.569 --> 09:37.303
HOW ARE YOU DOING,
VERONICA?

09:39.372 --> 09:41.808
I AM WONDERFUL.

09:41.808 --> 09:44.077
