A BETTER LIAR THAN THAT.

10:05.972 --> 10:08.875
NO, NO, NO. I MEAN IT.
I DO.

10:08.875 --> 10:11.377
OH.
I MEAN IT.

10:11.377 --> 10:14.515
I'M GLAD THAT YOU'RE OKAY.
WOULDN'T YOU LIKE TO THANK ME?

10:14.515 --> 10:15.816
NO.

10:15.816 --> 10:18.752
NO?

10:18.752 --> 10:20.587
SO HOW HAVE YOU BEEN DOING

10:20.587 --> 10:24.625
