SITUATION OF OURS?

10:24.625 --> 10:25.726
HMM?

10:25.726 --> 10:26.993
OH, YOU MEAN THE THING

10:26.993 --> 10:29.295
ABOUT KATHERYN MURDERING
THE D. A. IN COLD BLOOD.

10:29.295 --> 10:32.799
HEY, SHH, SHH, SHH.
YES, YEAH, YEAH.

10:32.799 --> 10:35.268
VERONICA, COME ON.

10:35.268 --> 10:37.070
YEAH.

10:37.070 --> 10:40.073
I'M STILL KEEPING
YOUR SECRET FOR NOW.

10:40.073 --> 10:43.243
♪♪♪♪

10:43.243 --> 10:44.778
WELL, ON BEHALF
OF KATHERYN AND I,

10:44.778 --> 10:47.514
I'D LIKE TO SAY THANK YOU.

10:47.514 --> 10:48.882
YOU KNOW THE D. A.'S OFFICE

10:48.882 --> 10:51.952
AND SEVERAL FEDERAL AGENTS
WILL BE LOOKING FOR HER.

10:51.952 --> 10:54.020
YES, I REALIZE THAT.

10:54.020 --> 10:56.957
THEN WHATEVER YOU TWO
ARE PLANNING,

10:56.957 --> 10:58.324
YOU NEED TO GET IT GOING.

10:58.324 --> 11:00.761
OH, WE WILL.

11:00.761 --> 11:05.171
NOT QUITE LIKE YOU DID
WITH YOUR SON, THOUGH.

11:05.171 --> 11:06.840
