IF YOU WOULD NOT MENTION MY SON.

11:09.409 --> 11:11.745
WELL...

11:11.745 --> 11:14.314
YOU DIDN'T HANDLE
THAT VERY WELL, DARLING.

11:14.314 --> 11:16.216
NO, BUT I'M HANDLING THIS.

11:16.216 --> 11:18.451
WELL, IF YOU'RE HANDLING IT,
THEN YOU NEED TO GO...

11:18.451 --> 11:19.953
I'M HANDLING THIS.

11:19.953 --> 11:22.355
OKAY. THEN, WHILE YOU'RE
HANDLING IT,

11:22.355 --> 11:24.424
