TO GO SEE YOUR SON.

11:26.727 --> 11:28.128
WHAT DO YOU ‐‐

11:28.128 --> 11:29.696
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, VERONICA?
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

11:29.696 --> 11:32.365
OH, CALM DOWN.
I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING TO HIM.

11:32.365 --> 11:33.700
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING
ABOUT, VERONICA?

11:33.700 --> 11:38.939
HE SEEMS HELL‐BENT ON WANTING
TO DO THAT TO HIMSELF.

11:38.939 --> 11:41.642
