WITH HIS DOCTOR.

12:08.942 --> 12:10.611
‐WHAT ROOM IS HE IN, MISS?
‐JUST ONE MOMENT.

12:10.611 --> 12:13.113
‐FIND OUT WHERE HE IS.
‐WHAT ROOM IS HE IN?

12:13.113 --> 12:14.447
I'M NOT ALLOWED TO SAY,

12:14.447 --> 12:16.617
BUT THE DOCTOR WILL BE HERE
IN ONE MOMENT.

12:16.617 --> 12:19.052
♪♪♪♪

12:19.052 --> 12:20.921
WHAT THE HELL, DAVID,
HUH?

12:26.527 --> 12:28.394
♪♪♪♪

