12:42.609 --> 12:43.744
WHY ARE YOU EVEN HERE?

12:43.744 --> 12:45.679
I ‐‐ I JUST WANTED TO SEE
IF YOU WERE OKAY.

12:45.679 --> 12:47.748
IF I'M OKAY?
YES.

12:47.748 --> 12:49.783
OF COURSE I'M NOT OKAY.

12:49.783 --> 12:50.984
I KNOW. I KNOW THAT.

12:50.984 --> 12:53.353
THEN WHY WOULD YOU SAY
SOMETHING SO STUPID?

12:53.353 --> 12:56.022
OKAY. OKAY.
I MEAN, YOU ‐‐

12:56.022 --> 12:57.390
YOU SHOULDN'T BE
GETTING UPSET.

12:57.390 --> 12:59.392
DON'T TELL ME WHAT TO DO.
I'M NOT. I'M ‐‐

12:59.392 --> 13:01.602
YOU AND YOUR BITCH
OF A MOTHER

13:01.602 --> 13:03.737
CAN'T TELL ME A DAMN THING.

13:03.737 --> 13:05.606
♪♪♪♪

13:05.606 --> 13:07.508
[ SIGHS ]

13:07.508 --> 13:08.975
MELISSA, I DO CARE.

13:08.975 --> 13:10.911
OKAY?

13:10.911 --> 13:13.614
SINCE WHEN?

13:13.614 --> 13:16.049
