LOOK. I KNOW THAT THINGS
ARE ROUGH, YOU KNOW?

13:22.756 --> 13:24.691
BUT, I MEAN,

13:24.691 --> 13:28.261
TAKING YOUR LIFE
IS NOT THE ANSWER.

13:28.261 --> 13:31.231
REALLY?
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:31.231 --> 13:33.634
NO. IT'S NOT.

13:33.634 --> 13:37.704
YOU'RE REALLY TRYING TO HELP ME,
JEFFERY, ANALYZE ME?

13:37.704 --> 13:39.706
NO. I'M JUST...

13:39.706 --> 13:42.676
JUST WASTING
YOUR DAMN TIME.

13:42.676 --> 13:46.079
OKAY?

13:46.079 --> 13:47.748
I JUST WANTED YOU TO KNOW.

13:47.748 --> 13:50.684
♪♪♪♪

13:50.684 --> 13:53.887
WANTED ME TO KNOW?

13:53.887 --> 13:55.889
TELL ME, PLEASE.

13:55.889 --> 13:58.224
TELL ME.

13:58.224 --> 14:03.136
THE ONLY PERSON WHO HAS
EVER LOVED ME IS DEAD,

14:03.136 --> 14:04.370
AND YOU WANT TO SAY SOMETHING

14:04.370 --> 14:08.274
TO MAKE ME FEEL BETTER,
CHEER ME UP?

14:08.274 --> 14:11.244
I MEAN, YOUR MOM
LOVES YOU, MELISSA.

14:11.244 --> 14:14.114
LIKE YOURS LOVES YOU.

14:14.114 --> 14:17.784
MY FATHER LOVED ME.

14:17.784 --> 14:20.320
♪♪♪♪

14:20.320 --> 14:24.324
‐I'M SORRY.
‐OH, NO, YOU'RE NOT.

14:24.324 --> 14:26.993
YOU'RE JUST LIKE
YOUR MOTHER.

14:26.993 --> 14:27.961
MELISSA...

14:27.961 --> 14:31.097
YOU ARE JUST LIKE
YOUR MOTHER.

14:31.097 --> 14:33.399
YOU BOTH JUST WANT
TO INFLICT PAIN.

14:33.399 --> 14:35.536
WELL, DAMN THAT.
I HAVE FEELINGS.

14:35.536 --> 14:37.003
DAMN THAT!
I'M A HUMAN BEING!

14:37.003 --> 14:38.338
HEY, ALL RIGHT.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

14:38.338 --> 14:39.305
YOU REALLY SHOULDN'T
BE GETTING UPSET.

14:39.305 --> 14:40.774
NO, YOU CAN JUST GO!

14:40.774 --> 14:42.676
I'M JUST ‐‐
I'M TRYING TO HELP.

14:42.676 --> 14:45.445
LEAVE! JUST LEAVE!

14:45.445 --> 14:48.481
♪♪♪♪

15:02.002 --> 15:03.837
[ SNIFFLES ]

15:07.207 --> 15:10.243
♪♪♪♪

15:26.492 --> 15:28.428
WHERE ARE WE?

15:28.428 --> 15:31.532
THIS IS ONE
OF MY RENTAL HOUSES.

15:31.532 --> 15:32.666
I MOVED IN YESTERDAY.

15:32.666 --> 15:35.802
HERE. TAKE THIS.

15:35.802 --> 15:37.671
WHAT IS THAT?

15:37.671 --> 15:40.841
IT'S SOMETHING
TO HELP YOU SLEEP.

15:40.841 --> 15:44.244
I DON'T WANT TO SLEEP.

15:44.244 --> 15:45.946
YOU NEED TO REST, HANNA.

15:45.946 --> 15:48.048
TRUST ME.

15:48.048 --> 15:51.084
IT'S THE ONLY THING
THAT'S GONNA HELP.

15:51.084 --> 15:52.252
TAKE IT.

15:56.156 --> 15:59.192
♪♪♪♪

16:03.103 --> 16:05.005
IT'S NOT GONNA WORK.

16:05.005 --> 16:06.339
IT'S STRONG.

16:09.209 --> 16:10.376
NOW, I'M SORRY.

16:10.376 --> 16:13.346
I DON'T HAVE ANYBODY HERE

16:13.346 --> 16:14.648
TO HELP ME CLEAN
THE GUEST ROOM,

16:14.648 --> 16:16.517
SO I HAD TO MAKE
IT UP MYSELF.

16:16.517 --> 16:20.053
IT MAY NOT BE
TOO COMFORTABLE.

16:20.053 --> 16:22.188
WHY ARE YOU STAYING HERE?

16:22.188 --> 16:24.625
MM.

16:24.625 --> 16:26.760
I'VE HAD ENOUGH OF JIM.
I'M DIVORCING HIM.

16:26.760 --> 16:29.730
WE'RE DONE, BUT THIS
ISN'T ABOUT THAT.

16:29.730 --> 16:32.465
THIS IS ABOUT YOU.

16:32.465 --> 16:35.669
I LEFT SOME CLOTHES
IN THERE FOR YOU TO USE.

16:35.669 --> 16:39.139
THEY MIGHT BE A LITTLE BIG,
BUT HELP YOURSELF.

16:39.139 --> 16:42.543
AND I SUGGEST YOU
TAKE A SHOWER

16:42.543 --> 16:43.844
BECAUSE ONCE THAT PILL
KICKS IN,

16:43.844 --> 16:45.679
I'M NOT EVEN GONNA BE ABLE
TO GET YOU UP OFF THE FLOOR.

16:45.679 --> 16:49.415
I DON'T WANT
TO TAKE A SHOWER.

16:49.415 --> 16:51.217
HANNA.

16:51.217 --> 16:52.553
I DON'T.

16:55.388 --> 16:58.024
♪♪♪♪

16:58.024 --> 16:59.560
LOOK AT YOUR HANDS.

17:02.468 --> 17:05.506
♪♪♪♪

17:09.075 --> 17:11.144
[ Voice breaking ]
OH, MY LORD.

17:11.144 --> 17:12.979
[ CRIES ]

17:18.585 --> 17:19.886
OH, MY GOD.

17:19.886 --> 17:22.956
[ SOBS ]

17:22.956 --> 17:25.592
SHH.
MY BABY'S BLOOD.

17:27.160 --> 17:29.295
I'M SORRY.

17:29.295 --> 17:31.164
♪♪♪♪

17:31.164 --> 17:33.299
I'M SORRY.

17:36.503 --> 17:39.540
♪♪♪♪

17:44.878 --> 17:47.247
MY FAITH WAS
ALL I HAD, KATHERYN.

17:49.282 --> 17:51.317
IT'S ALL I HAD.

17:53.453 --> 17:57.924
YOU STILL HAVE IT.

17:57.924 --> 18:01.201
THIS IS KILLING ME.

18:01.201 --> 18:04.838
AND IT'S CRUMBLING
IN MY SOUL.

18:04.838 --> 18:07.073
I KNOW.

18:07.073 --> 18:08.441
I KNOW.

18:10.777 --> 18:13.246
IT IS.

18:13.246 --> 18:16.049
[ CRIES ]

18:16.049 --> 18:17.751
IN THAT VERY MOMENT
I MET YOU,

18:17.751 --> 18:20.921
I KNEW THAT YOU BELIEVE
STRONGLY IN GOD.

18:20.921 --> 18:23.824
♪♪♪♪

18:23.824 --> 18:26.993
YOU EVEN PRAYED FOR ME.

18:26.993 --> 18:29.796
I KNOW THAT THIS IS TRAGIC.

18:29.796 --> 18:33.366
I KNOW IT.

18:33.366 --> 18:36.870
BUT I ALSO KNOW
THAT YOUR FAITH

18:36.870 --> 18:41.708
IS TOO STRONG
TO LET ANYTHING SHAKE IT,

18:41.708 --> 18:45.011
EVEN SOMETHING AS SAD
AND AS SENSELESS AS THIS.

18:45.011 --> 18:47.648
♪♪♪♪

18:47.648 --> 18:50.116
I ‐‐ I DON'T KNOW
HOW IT'S NOT.

18:50.116 --> 18:52.352
I'M ONLY HUMAN,

18:52.352 --> 18:55.321
AND I GOT TO BURY
MY GRANDSON.

18:55.321 --> 18:56.557
[ SOBS ]

18:56.557 --> 18:58.124
I DON'T KNOW HOW IT'S NOT.

18:58.124 --> 18:59.760
I AM SO ANGRY!

18:59.760 --> 19:01.301
I AM SO ANGRY!

19:01.301 --> 19:05.672
BREATHE. BREATHE.
BREATHE.

19:05.672 --> 19:08.675
JUST TELL YOURSELF
TO BREATHE.

19:08.675 --> 19:10.210
JUST BREATHE.

19:10.210 --> 19:13.246
♪♪♪♪

19:17.283 --> 19:19.485
COME ON.
LET'S ‐‐

19:19.485 --> 19:22.488
LET'S GET YOU CLEANED UP,
OKAY,

19:22.488 --> 19:24.190
BEFORE THAT PILL KICKS IN.

19:24.190 --> 19:27.227
ALL RIGHT?
COME ON.

19:27.227 --> 19:30.430
COME ON.

19:30.430 --> 19:33.333
COME ON.

19:33.333 --> 19:35.869
COME ON.

19:35.869 --> 19:37.704
I GOT YOU.

19:37.704 --> 19:38.972
I GOT YOU.

19:41.441 --> 19:44.477
♪♪♪♪

19:58.024 --> 20:01.001
[ CRIES ]

20:06.573 --> 20:09.610
♪♪♪♪

20:39.506 --> 20:42.543
♪♪♪♪

21:02.836 --> 21:04.638
[ DOOR OPENS ]

21:08.742 --> 21:11.778
♪♪♪♪

21:14.881 --> 21:16.382
HOW IS
HE DOING?

21:16.382 --> 21:17.818
HE'S GONNA BE OKAY.

21:17.818 --> 21:20.253
OH, MAN. I FEEL SO SICK.

21:20.253 --> 21:21.487
YOU'RE GONNA KICK IT.

21:21.487 --> 21:22.689
I CAN'T DO IT, MAN.

21:22.689 --> 21:25.325
YES, YOU CAN.
YOU CAN DO IT.

21:25.325 --> 21:27.594
JEFFERY, JUST DON'T LEAVE.
ALL RIGHT?

21:27.594 --> 21:28.829
I'LL GIVE YOU A MOMENT.

21:28.829 --> 21:31.031
OKAY. THANKS.

21:31.031 --> 21:34.067
♪♪♪♪

21:36.503 --> 21:37.538
HEY, MAN.

21:37.538 --> 21:39.506
YOU SURE THESE PEOPLE
CAN HELP ME?

21:39.506 --> 21:41.642
I KNOW THEY CAN.

21:41.642 --> 21:43.677
MAN, MAN, I'M TRYING.

21:43.677 --> 21:45.879
I KNOW.
HEY, I KNOW, MAN,

21:45.879 --> 21:48.248
AND I'M PROUD
OF YOU FOR TRYING.

21:48.248 --> 21:50.350
MAN, I DON'T KNOW
IF I CAN DO IT.

21:50.350 --> 21:53.053
I CAN'T DO IT.

21:53.053 --> 21:55.288
WYATT, I KNOW
YOU CAN DO THIS.

21:55.288 --> 21:58.458
OKAY? YOU'RE STRONGER
THAN YOU THINK.

21:58.458 --> 22:00.894
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT THAT.

22:00.894 --> 22:02.903
I'VE NEVER HAD
TO BE STRONG BEFORE.

22:02.903 --> 22:05.305
WELL, THAT DOESN'T MEAN
THAT YOU AREN'T.

22:05.305 --> 22:07.340
I FEEL SO SICK, MAN.
I FEEL SO SICK.

22:07.340 --> 22:08.909
I KNOW. IT PASSES.

22:08.909 --> 22:12.278
IT'S ‐‐ LOOKIT, MAN.
IT'S NEVER BEEN THIS BAD BEFORE.

22:12.278 --> 22:14.915
YOU KNOW, WYATT, HEY,
IT WAS THIS BAD.

22:14.915 --> 22:16.983
REMEMBER WHEN WE WERE
AT THE FACILITY?

22:16.983 --> 22:18.685
IT WAS THIS BAD.

22:20.854 --> 22:23.289
I DON'T EVER REMEMBER IT
BEING THAT BAD.

22:23.289 --> 22:25.225
IT WAS, MAN.

22:25.225 --> 22:27.127
JUST ‐‐ JUST GIVE ME
SOMETHING, MAN.

22:27.127 --> 22:28.562
THEY NEED TO GIVE ME
SOMETHING.

22:28.562 --> 22:30.230
OKAY?
I'M ‐‐ I'M SURE THEY WILL.

22:30.230 --> 22:32.465
JUST ‐‐ JUST TELL THEM
TO GIVE ME SOMETHING.

22:32.465 --> 22:34.467
I NEED SOMETHING.
HEY, THEY HAVE A PLAN.

22:34.467 --> 22:36.336
ALL RIGHT? I KNOW THEY DO.
JUST STAY.

22:36.336 --> 22:38.004
OKAY? JUST STAY.
OKAY.

22:38.004 --> 22:40.073
OKAY. I'M HERE. I'M HERE.

22:40.073 --> 22:43.009
DAMN IT, MAN.
YOU'RE OKAY.

22:43.009 --> 22:45.078
YOU'RE OKAY.
I'M FR‐FREEZING, MAN.

22:45.078 --> 22:47.681
OKAY. LET ME, UM, LET ME
GO GET YOU A BLANKET.

22:47.681 --> 22:50.283
UH, WELL, NO, I MEAN ‐‐
NO, DON'T LEAVE ME, MAN.

22:50.283 --> 22:51.585
I'LL BE RIGHT OUT HERE.

22:51.585 --> 22:52.886
I'LL BE RIGHT OUT HERE,
AND I'LL COME RIGHT BACK.

22:52.886 --> 22:54.087
ALL RIGHT.
JEFFERY!

22:54.087 --> 22:55.689
HEY, I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.
NO, JEFFERY.

22:55.689 --> 22:57.323
COME ON, MAN.

22:57.323 --> 22:59.560
♪♪♪♪

22:59.560 --> 23:02.669
JEFFERY, JEFFERY!

23:02.669 --> 23:04.304
AH.

23:06.873 --> 23:09.910
♪♪♪♪

23:14.581 --> 23:15.882
OH, EXCUSE ME.

23:15.882 --> 23:17.684
CAN I HAVE SOME
BLANKETS, PLEASE?

23:17.684 --> 23:20.721
♪♪♪♪

23:22.656 --> 23:23.690
THANK YOU.

23:30.764 --> 23:32.866
SURE.
SURE, YEAH, THAT'D BE GOOD.

23:32.866 --> 23:35.902
♪♪♪♪

23:57.223 --> 24:00.233
♪♪♪♪

24:08.842 --> 24:11.477
ALL RIGHT.
HOLD ON ONE SECOND.

24:11.477 --> 24:14.515
♪♪♪♪

24:16.216 --> 24:17.918
JUST HANG TIGHT.

24:22.288 --> 24:23.289
IS THAT BETTER?

24:23.289 --> 24:24.725
NO.

24:24.725 --> 24:27.694
♪♪♪♪

24:27.694 --> 24:29.429
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

24:31.598 --> 24:33.934
HEY, CAN I TALK TO YOU?

24:33.934 --> 24:35.335
I'M BUSY.

24:35.335 --> 24:36.336
IT'LL ONLY TAKE A SECOND.

24:36.336 --> 24:38.071
I'M BUSY.

24:38.071 --> 24:39.840
YEAH. I SEE THAT.

24:39.840 --> 24:42.208
JUSTIN, I WILL CALL YOU.

24:42.208 --> 24:43.777
NOW IS NOT THE TIME.

24:43.777 --> 24:45.211
WHAT'S UP WITH
THIS GUY, MAN?

24:45.211 --> 24:47.013
HEY, JUST ‐‐

24:47.013 --> 24:49.550
JUST STAY STRONG.

24:49.550 --> 24:51.151
I NEED YOU TO LEAVE,
MAN.

24:51.151 --> 24:54.487
♪♪♪♪

24:54.487 --> 24:56.823
I'LL CALL YOU.

24:56.823 --> 24:59.025
I'LL JUST WAIT OUTSIDE.

24:59.025 --> 25:00.661
IT'S GONNA BE A WHILE.

25:00.661 --> 25:02.603
THAT'S FINE.
I'LL WAIT.

25:05.806 --> 25:08.441
♪♪♪♪

25:08.441 --> 25:10.076
WHAT THE HELL,
JEFFERY?

25:10.076 --> 25:12.613
IT'S FINE.

25:12.613 --> 25:14.214
THIS GUY IS NUTS.

25:17.050 --> 25:19.920
WHAT THE HELL, MAN?

25:19.920 --> 25:22.355
IT'S FINE.

25:22.355 --> 25:23.423
THAT GUY IS NUTS.

25:23.423 --> 25:26.660
COVER UP.

25:26.660 --> 25:28.061
NOW, JUST REST.

25:28.061 --> 25:31.197
ALL RIGHT?
I CAN'T, MAN.

25:31.197 --> 25:34.267
DID THEY GIVE YOU ANYTHING
TO HELP WITH THE SLEEP, MAN?

25:34.267 --> 25:35.802
YEAH, MAN. BUT IT'S ‐‐

25:35.802 --> 25:38.772
IT'S NOT WORKING.

25:38.772 --> 25:42.408
WELL, HOW LONG AGO
DID THEY GIVE IT TO YOU?

25:42.408 --> 25:44.745
I DON'T KNOW, LIKE,
20 MINUTES AGO OR SOMETHING?

25:44.745 --> 25:47.548
WOW, OKAY. WELL, JUST ‐‐
JUST GIVE IT SOME TIME.

25:47.548 --> 25:49.249
YEAH.
YEAH.

25:49.249 --> 25:50.617
BUT IT'S NOT WORKING.

25:50.617 --> 25:53.186
HEY, CAN YOU
PLEASE CALM DOWN?

25:53.186 --> 25:56.422
ALL RIGHT?
THANK YOU, MAN.

25:56.422 --> 25:58.124
THANK YOU.

25:58.124 --> 26:00.527
LISTEN, MAN.
I'M SORRY.

26:00.527 --> 26:02.302
I'M SORRY FOR TREATING
YOU LIKE CRAP.

26:02.302 --> 26:03.537
I...

26:03.537 --> 26:06.507
I KNOW. I'M HERE.

26:06.507 --> 26:10.243
OKAY? IT'S ‐‐ IT'S OKAY.

26:10.243 --> 26:14.480
YOU'RE THE ONLY FRIEND
THAT I GOT.

26:14.480 --> 26:17.684
AND I CAN'T EVEN GET YOU
TO STAY.

26:17.684 --> 26:19.085
YOU'RE OKAY.

26:19.085 --> 26:20.220
IT'S ‐‐ IT'S OKAY.

26:20.220 --> 26:22.222
NO, MAN.

26:22.222 --> 26:24.925
NO, IT'S NOT OKAY.

26:24.925 --> 26:26.727
I KNOW. IT'S...

26:26.727 --> 26:29.095
JUST RELAX.
ALL RIGHT?

26:29.095 --> 26:32.498
OH, GOD. I'M FREEZING.

26:32.498 --> 26:34.234
OKAY. WELL, THIS IS
AN ELECTRIC BLANKET.

26:34.234 --> 26:35.368
LOOK. I HAVE...

26:35.368 --> 26:37.504
HEY, HEY, HEY,
JUST DON'T LEAVE ME.

26:37.504 --> 26:39.372
OKAY?
OKAY. OKAY.

26:39.372 --> 26:41.041
I WON'T.
JUST DON'T LEAVE ME, PLEASE?

26:41.041 --> 26:43.043
I WON'T.
PLEASE, MAN.

26:43.043 --> 26:45.211
I WON'T. I WON'T.
KEEP COVERED.

26:45.211 --> 26:48.982
YOU HAVE TO KEEP
THE BLANKET ON YOU, PLEASE.

26:48.982 --> 26:52.385
HEY, MAN.
LISTEN.

26:52.385 --> 26:54.588
IF I GO TO SLEEP,

26:54.588 --> 26:56.990
ARE YOU GONNA BE HERE
WHEN I WAKE UP?

26:56.990 --> 26:58.725
WYATT, REST.

26:58.725 --> 27:03.036
PROMISE ME,
JEFFERY.

27:03.036 --> 27:04.270
I WILL.
YOU PROMISE?

27:04.270 --> 27:07.040
I WILL. I WILL.

27:07.040 --> 27:09.075
THANK YOU.
IT'S OKAY.

27:09.075 --> 27:10.644
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

27:10.644 --> 27:13.379
I DON'T WANT TO DIE.

27:13.379 --> 27:15.616
YOU'RE NOT GONNA DIE.

27:15.616 --> 27:17.183
I DON'T WANT TO DIE, MAN.

27:17.183 --> 27:18.652
I TOLD YOU,
YOU'RE NOT GONNA DIE.

27:18.652 --> 27:19.853
YOU PROMISE?
YES.

27:19.853 --> 27:21.121
YOU'RE GONNA KICK IT.

27:21.121 --> 27:23.590
LISTEN.
I WAS SCARED, MAN.

27:23.590 --> 27:25.926
I WAS SCARED WHEN I OD'D.

27:25.926 --> 27:28.562
LISTEN, MAN.
I ‐‐ I WAS GOING CRAZY.

27:28.562 --> 27:30.096
I KNOW.

27:30.096 --> 27:33.534
I KNOW. BUT I'M HERE.

27:33.534 --> 27:34.835
LISTEN, MAN.
JUST DON'T LEAVE ME.

27:34.835 --> 27:36.269
OKAY?
I'M NOT. I'M NOT.

27:36.269 --> 27:38.739
I'M NOT.
JUST ‐‐

27:38.739 --> 27:40.707
SHH, SHH, SHH, SHH.

27:40.707 --> 27:42.876
YOU'RE GONNA STAY, RIGHT?
YOU'RE GONNA STAY?

27:42.876 --> 27:45.812
YES. JUST COVER UP.

27:49.349 --> 27:51.585
[ BEEPS ]

28:01.001 --> 28:02.302
WAKE UP.

28:02.302 --> 28:04.705
♪♪♪♪

28:04.705 --> 28:05.672
NOW WHAT?

28:05.672 --> 28:07.641
THAT'S $250,000
RIGHT THERE.

28:07.641 --> 28:08.975
GOT YOUR ATTENTION NOW?

28:14.981 --> 28:17.250
IT'S ALREADY MINE.
YOU TOOK IT.

28:17.250 --> 28:19.686
NO, IT'S NOT. IT'S JIM CRYER'S,
AND YOU KNOW IT.

28:19.686 --> 28:21.021
IT'S MINE.

28:21.021 --> 28:23.624
WELL, THIS IS A CHANCE
FOR YOU TO EARN IT RIGHT NOW.

28:23.624 --> 28:24.891
I DON'T TRUST YOU.

28:24.891 --> 28:28.361
ALL I NEED YOU TO DO
IS GIVE ME WHAT YOU GOT.

28:28.361 --> 28:29.630
I DON'T HAVE ANYTHING.

28:29.630 --> 28:31.364
CANDACE, LOOK.
I COULD HAVE GONE TO THE POLICE,

28:31.364 --> 28:32.666
COULD HAVE TIPPED YOU OFF,

28:32.666 --> 28:34.601
TOLD THEM WHERE YOU WERE,
BUT I DIDN'T.

28:34.601 --> 28:37.070
HEY, I'M TRYING TO GET US
TO WORK TOGETHER.

28:37.070 --> 28:39.405
I WILL NEVER
WORK WITH YOU.

28:39.405 --> 28:40.974
YOU'RE GONNA WALK AWAY
FROM THIS MONEY?

28:40.974 --> 28:42.943
OH, NO.
I'M TAKING THE MONEY.

28:42.943 --> 28:46.379
CANDACE.
OH, EVERY DOLLAR, I PROMISE.

28:46.379 --> 28:47.814
AND HOW THE HELL ARE YOU
GOING TO GET IT FROM ME?

28:47.814 --> 28:51.652
YOU DON'T THINK I WILL GIVE YOU
ANOTHER KNOT ON YOUR HEAD?

28:51.652 --> 28:53.587
‐CANDACE.
‐I'M A GIRL FROM THE STREETS,

28:53.587 --> 28:56.322
AND I HAVE FOUGHT BIGGER DEVILS
THAN YOU AND WON.

28:56.322 --> 28:57.758
OKAY.
I DON'T WANT TO FIGHT.

28:57.758 --> 28:59.125
GOOD.

28:59.125 --> 29:00.827
NOW LEAVE.
OKAY.

29:00.827 --> 29:02.669
BUT I'M TAKING THE MONEY.
NO.

29:02.669 --> 29:03.970
CANDACE.
YOU'RE LEAVING THE MONEY.

29:03.970 --> 29:04.905
CANDACE, LET IT GO.

29:04.905 --> 29:07.140
AND YOU OWE ME ANOTHER 3.7.

29:09.743 --> 29:12.245
CANDACE, CANDACE, STOP.

29:12.245 --> 29:13.346
YOU'RE SO DAMN STUPID.

29:13.346 --> 29:15.015
DON'T YOU SEE
WHAT'S HAPPENED HERE?

29:15.015 --> 29:17.317
NO. GET OFF.

29:17.317 --> 29:19.185
YOU KNOW WHAT I SEE?

29:19.185 --> 29:20.887
A GUY WHO'S ABOUT
TO BECOME THE PRESIDENT,

29:20.887 --> 29:22.889
WHO IS A GOOD MAN,

29:22.889 --> 29:24.625
WHO HAS KIDS,

29:24.625 --> 29:26.893
AND YOU'RE TRYING
TO DESTROY THAT.

29:26.893 --> 29:30.096
WAIT. WHAT IS THIS,
A WHORE WITH A HEART?

29:30.096 --> 29:33.133
YEAH. AND I COULD BE ONE
WITH A GUN, TOO.

29:33.133 --> 29:34.668
DO YOU WANT TO LAY ON YOUR BACK
FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE?

29:34.668 --> 29:36.336
OSCAR.
LOOK.

29:36.336 --> 29:37.971
YOU'RE NOT GETTING
ANY YOUNGER.

29:37.971 --> 29:39.339
I COULD HAVE USED
A LOT MORE GIRLS

29:39.339 --> 29:40.807
FOR THIS
FOR A LOT LESS MONEY,

29:40.807 --> 29:42.676
I MIGHT ADD.

29:42.676 --> 29:44.210
THEN DO IT.
THEY'RE NOT YOU.

29:44.210 --> 29:46.613
EXACTLY. THEY'RE NOT ME.

29:46.613 --> 29:50.483
AND THAT COMMENT ABOUT I'M NOT
GETTING ANY YOUNGER, SHOVE IT.

29:50.483 --> 29:53.319
CANDACE, I JUST WANT
YOU TO HELP ME.

29:53.319 --> 29:54.621
NO.

29:54.621 --> 29:57.223
CANDACE, YOU DON'T WANT
TO BE THE FIRST LADY?

29:57.223 --> 29:58.391
[ SCOFFS ] IN 8 YEARS?

29:58.391 --> 30:00.460
‐CANDACE, PLAY THE LONG GAME.
‐I TOLD YOU.

30:00.460 --> 30:02.903
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT THIS WOULD MEAN?

30:02.903 --> 30:05.706
I AM NOT INTERESTED
IN LIVING IN AN OLD HOUSE

30:05.706 --> 30:07.674
WITH A BUNCH
OF ARROGANT POLITICIANS.

30:07.674 --> 30:09.710
AND YOU KNOW WHAT?
NEITHER IS HE.

30:09.710 --> 30:11.344
WAIT. WAIT.
DID HE SAY THAT?

30:11.344 --> 30:13.113
OSCAR.
NO, NO, I'M SERIOUS.

30:13.113 --> 30:15.649
THIS IS GOOD STUFF.
WHAT ELSE DID HE SAY?

30:17.984 --> 30:20.954
I AM NOT GIVING YOU
THAT MAN.

30:20.954 --> 30:23.089
SO YOU CAN LEAVE NOW.
OKAY.

30:23.089 --> 30:25.225
WELL, I'M GONNA TAKE
MY MONEY WITH ME.

30:25.225 --> 30:27.160
NO. YOU THINK SO?

30:27.160 --> 30:29.563
WATCH ME.
GET OUT.

30:29.563 --> 30:31.264
ALL YOU HAVE TO DO
IS SAY, "YES."

30:31.264 --> 30:32.633
THE MONEY IS YOURS.
OKAY. OKAY. OKAY.

30:32.633 --> 30:34.134
OKAY.
LET GO.

30:34.134 --> 30:36.903
YES, YES, YES.

30:36.903 --> 30:39.439
YOU'RE LYING.
NO, I'M NOT.

30:39.439 --> 30:42.576
YES, YOU ARE. I KNOW YOU.

30:42.576 --> 30:43.810
YOU KNOW WHAT?

30:43.810 --> 30:45.646
I ASKED YOU IF YOU
HAD MONEY YESTERDAY,

30:45.646 --> 30:47.080
AND YOU SAID NO.

30:47.080 --> 30:50.183
THEN YOU WALK IN HERE TODAY
WITH $250,000, SO OKAY,

30:50.183 --> 30:51.918
I'LL DO IT.
I WENT TO MY CLIENTS,

30:51.918 --> 30:53.486
AND I TOLD THEM
I NEEDED SOME CASH.

30:53.486 --> 30:57.323
THEY'RE EXPECTING RESULTS.
OKAY.

30:57.323 --> 30:59.292
CANDACE, THIS IS
A PRIVATE SUPER PAC

30:59.292 --> 31:03.003
WHO NEED THEIR GUY TO WIN.

31:03.003 --> 31:04.437
THAT HAS NOTHING
TO DO WITH ME.

31:04.437 --> 31:06.807
YOU DON'T WANT TO MESS
WITH THESE PEOPLE.

31:06.807 --> 31:09.876
I DON'T KNOW THEM.
CANDACE.

31:09.876 --> 31:11.244
WHAT?

31:11.244 --> 31:14.881
I TOLD YOU, I'LL DO IT.

31:14.881 --> 31:16.449
OH, I GET IT.

31:16.449 --> 31:18.384
GOOD.

31:18.384 --> 31:19.620
YOU'RE TRYING
TO DO THIS ON YOUR OWN.

31:19.620 --> 31:22.623
YOU'RE TRYING
TO BLACKMAIL HIM.

31:22.623 --> 31:24.825
CANDACE, LET ME WARN YOU.

31:24.825 --> 31:26.693
YOU DON'T HAVE TO WARN ME
ABOUT NOTHING.

31:26.693 --> 31:28.862
DO NOT TRY TO GO
AT THIS ALONE.

31:28.862 --> 31:30.163
WHY NOT?

31:30.163 --> 31:31.932
YOU DON'T GET IT, DO YOU?

31:31.932 --> 31:35.001
HE'S GONNA BE PRESIDENT.

31:35.001 --> 31:37.170
ALL THE MORE REASON WHY
HE'LL PAY ME TO GO AWAY.

31:37.170 --> 31:39.640
HE DOESN'T HAVE ANY MONEY.
HE HAS VERY LITTLE MONEY.

31:39.640 --> 31:42.442
WE'LL HAVE TO FIND IT.

31:42.442 --> 31:44.911
[ SCOFFS ] YOU ARE JUST
DOWNRIGHT STUPID.

31:44.911 --> 31:46.379
CALL ME STUPID AGAIN.

31:46.379 --> 31:47.748
CANDACE, LISTEN TO ME.

31:47.748 --> 31:49.916
YOU THINK THAT
THE PRESIDENCY IS WON?

31:49.916 --> 31:51.752
NO. THESE THINGS
ARE BOUGHT AND SOLD.

31:51.752 --> 31:54.187
THESE PEOPLE ARE
POSITIONED AND CREATED.

31:54.187 --> 31:55.922
WE ARE TALKING ABOUT
BILLIONS OF DOLLARS.

31:55.922 --> 31:57.858
THIS ISN'T A LEAGUE
YOU KNOW HOW TO PLAY IN.

31:57.858 --> 31:59.826
NOW, JUST LIKE YOUR GUY
HAS A SUPER PAC,

31:59.826 --> 32:01.935
SO DOES MINE,
AND A LOT OF PEOPLE HAVE

32:01.935 --> 32:03.604
A VESTED INTEREST
IN HIM WINNING,

32:03.604 --> 32:05.872
AND IF THEY SMELL YOU COMING OR
THEY FEEL THREATENED BY YOU,

32:05.872 --> 32:08.108
THEY WILL COME FOR YOU.

32:08.108 --> 32:10.577
SO PLEASE TELL ME
YOU DIDN'T DO THIS.

32:10.577 --> 32:14.280
PLEASE?

32:14.280 --> 32:16.717
BYE.

32:16.717 --> 32:17.951
YOU DID.

32:17.951 --> 32:19.553
DAMN IT.

32:19.553 --> 32:21.054
BYE.

32:21.054 --> 32:22.355
I CAN'T USE YOU NOW.

32:22.355 --> 32:25.792
YOU'RE DAMAGED.
I'M TAKING MY MONEY.

32:25.792 --> 32:27.561
NO, YOU'RE NOT.
JUST LET IT GO.

32:27.561 --> 32:28.829
NO.
LET IT GO.

32:28.829 --> 32:30.463
I'M TAKING MY MONEY.
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

32:30.463 --> 32:32.132
I'LL SCREAM.
YOU THINK I WON'T?

32:32.132 --> 32:33.667
SECRET SERVICE
IS RIGHT DOWN THE HALL.

32:33.667 --> 32:35.201
I DON'T CARE.
DROP IT.

32:35.201 --> 32:36.169
NO.

32:36.169 --> 32:37.137
HELP!

32:37.137 --> 32:38.071
OKAY.
OKAY.

32:38.071 --> 32:40.206
HELP!

32:40.206 --> 32:41.775
SOMEONE!

32:43.944 --> 32:46.212
♪♪♪♪

32:56.122 --> 32:59.159
♪♪♪♪

33:06.472 --> 33:08.875
SON OF A BITCH.

33:13.213 --> 33:14.748
[ DOOR OPENS ]

33:19.285 --> 33:21.321
‐HOW IS HE?
‐SLEEPING.

33:21.321 --> 33:22.689
GOOD.

33:24.224 --> 33:25.659
THANK YOU.

33:25.659 --> 33:27.761
NO, THANK YOU.

33:27.761 --> 33:30.496
I COULDN'T GET HIM
TO CALM DOWN.

33:30.496 --> 33:33.299
HE REALLY LOVES YOU.

33:33.299 --> 33:36.436
OH, YEAH,
BUT IT'S NOT LIKE THAT.

33:36.436 --> 33:38.204
LIKE WHAT?

33:38.204 --> 33:40.340
HE'S NOT GAY.

33:40.340 --> 33:44.477
AND DOES HE HAVE TO BE GAY
TO LOVE YOU, HMM?

33:44.477 --> 33:45.712
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

33:45.712 --> 33:47.881
NO.
OF COURSE NOT.

33:47.881 --> 33:51.184
HE LOVES YOU,
AND I KNOW YOU LOVE HIM.

33:51.184 --> 33:54.621
WELL, HE'S GOT A GOOD HEART
UNDER ALL THAT PAIN.

33:54.621 --> 33:55.856
YEAH.

33:55.856 --> 33:58.391
I SENSE THAT.
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:00.861 --> 34:03.870
ALL RIGHT.
UM, I'M GONNA GO HOME.

34:03.870 --> 34:07.407
YOU KNOW, HE'S GONNA BE
LOOKING FOR YOU, RIGHT?

34:07.407 --> 34:09.475
YEAH. WELL,
I DON'T WANT TO TRADE

34:09.475 --> 34:11.945
ONE DEPENDENCY FOR ANOTHER.

34:11.945 --> 34:14.681
AND WHAT WOULD THAT BE?

34:14.681 --> 34:17.317
ME.

34:17.317 --> 34:19.352
YEAH.
I'VE SEEN THAT BEFORE.

34:19.352 --> 34:22.422
THEY TRADE DEPENDENCIES.

34:22.422 --> 34:24.324
HMM.

34:24.324 --> 34:28.128
I JUST WANT HIM TO BE ABLE
TO STAND ON HIS OWN.

34:28.128 --> 34:29.362
VERY SMART.

34:29.362 --> 34:30.597
THAT'S GOOD.

34:34.300 --> 34:37.838
UH, IS THAT COP
STILL OUT THERE.

34:37.838 --> 34:39.640
YEAH. THERE'S
A COP OUT THERE.

34:39.640 --> 34:41.708
HE'S BEEN THERE FOR,
LIKE, AN HOUR.

34:41.708 --> 34:43.476
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

34:43.476 --> 34:44.477
YEAH, YEAH.

34:44.477 --> 34:46.547
HMM, ARE YOU SURE?

34:46.547 --> 34:49.315
YEAH, YEAH.
YEAH, I'M SURE.

34:49.315 --> 34:51.084
THANK YOU, ANNA.

34:51.084 --> 34:52.185
I'LL SEE YOU TOMORROW.

34:52.185 --> 34:54.120
YEAH. I'LL SEE
YOU TOMORROW.

34:56.923 --> 34:59.960
♪♪♪♪

35:03.236 --> 35:06.740
HEY.

35:06.740 --> 35:08.341
YOU'RE STILL HERE.

35:08.341 --> 35:10.811
YEAH.
WHY?

35:10.811 --> 35:14.114
BECAUSE I WANT
TO TALK TO YOU.

35:14.114 --> 35:15.649
JUSTIN, LOOK.

35:15.649 --> 35:17.017
I'M NOT...
NO, REALLY.

35:17.017 --> 35:18.952
I JUST WANT TO TALK.

35:18.952 --> 35:21.087
[ SIGHS ]

35:21.087 --> 35:25.491
OKAY. WHAT DO YOU WANT
TO TALK ABOUT?

35:25.491 --> 35:26.860
NOT HERE.

35:26.860 --> 35:28.662
NO. WE SHOULD TALK HERE.

35:28.662 --> 35:30.196
JEFFERY, YOU KNOW
I DON'T WANT TO TALK

35:30.196 --> 35:31.832
ABOUT THIS STUFF RIGHT HERE.

35:31.832 --> 35:35.602
WELL, THEN YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE TO CALL ME.

35:35.602 --> 35:37.571
JEFFERY. PLEASE.
NO, NO.

35:37.571 --> 35:39.339
I DON'T WANT TO GO
ANYWHERE WITH YOU.

35:39.339 --> 35:41.474
COME ON.
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

35:41.474 --> 35:43.910
OKAY.
FINE.

35:43.910 --> 35:45.278
I'M SORRY.

35:45.278 --> 35:47.147
I WAS OUT OF CONTROL.

35:47.147 --> 35:49.783
IT'LL NEVER HAPPEN
AGAIN, EVER.

35:52.418 --> 35:54.387
JUSTIN.

35:54.387 --> 35:56.489
PLEASE, JEFFERY.

35:58.825 --> 36:00.060
PLEASE?

36:00.060 --> 36:03.103
♪♪♪♪

36:15.348 --> 36:18.384
♪♪♪♪

36:42.108 --> 36:43.910
NO, NO, NO.

36:43.910 --> 36:45.478
IT'S FINE.
THERE'S NO CAMERAS IN HERE.

36:45.478 --> 36:47.548
I ALREADY CHECKED.

36:47.548 --> 36:49.482
I THINK
I NEED CAMERAS WITH YOU.

36:49.482 --> 36:51.718
NO, YOU DON'T.

36:51.718 --> 36:53.854
AFTER WHAT YOU PULLED?

36:53.854 --> 36:57.624
I SAID I'M SORRY.

36:57.624 --> 36:59.092
OKAY.

36:59.092 --> 37:01.367
YOU DON'T NEED
TO BE AFRAID OF ME.

37:01.367 --> 37:03.169
I'M NOT.

37:03.169 --> 37:05.104
I'M JUST...

37:05.104 --> 37:06.205
I ACCEPT YOUR APOLOGY.

37:06.205 --> 37:08.174
OKAY. LISTEN.

37:08.174 --> 37:10.510
I DIDN'T KNOW
HE WAS YOUR FRIEND,

37:10.510 --> 37:13.947
SO SEEING YOU WITH HIM
MADE ME A LITTLE CRAZY.

37:13.947 --> 37:17.050
EVEN TODAY, IT MADE ME
A LITTLE CRAZY.

37:17.050 --> 37:19.085
I CAN BE A LITTLE
JEALOUS AT TIMES.

37:19.085 --> 37:22.022
IT'S... SEE, IT'S NOT
EVEN LIKE THAT.

37:22.022 --> 37:24.558
I STILL DON'T LIKE IT.
HE'S MY FRIEND.

37:24.558 --> 37:25.759
WE HAVE BEEN FRIENDS
SINCE WE WERE...

37:25.759 --> 37:27.694
YEAH, SINCE YOU WERE KIDS.
YOU SAID THAT.

37:27.694 --> 37:30.597
YES. AND, JUSTIN,
WE'RE NOT TOGETHER,

37:30.597 --> 37:34.134
SO I CAN SEE WHOEVER
I WANT, AND I WILL.

37:34.134 --> 37:36.336
DON'T SAY THAT, JEFFERY.

37:36.336 --> 37:37.538
"DON'T SAY ‐‐
DON'T SAY THAT"?

37:37.538 --> 37:40.741
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"DON'T SAY THAT"?

37:40.741 --> 37:43.777
LOOK. I THINK WE'RE ON TWO
TOTALLY DIFFERENT PAGES.

37:43.777 --> 37:45.445
ALL RIGHT?
AND I DON'T WANT TO BE IN.

37:45.445 --> 37:49.382
DON'T EVEN TELL ME YOU DON'T
WANT TO SEE ME ANYMORE.

37:49.382 --> 37:51.417
NO, I'M NOT SAYING THAT.
JEFFERY.

37:51.417 --> 37:54.521
I'M JUST SAYING THAT THINGS
ARE MOVING A LITTLE TOO FAST,

37:54.521 --> 37:56.122
AND MAYBE WE SHOULD
TAKE A STEP BACK

37:56.122 --> 37:59.526
AND JUST SEE
WHAT'S HAPPENING.

37:59.526 --> 38:02.135
ALL RIGHT. YOU'RE HURT
FROM WHAT I DID.

38:02.135 --> 38:03.570
I AM.

38:03.570 --> 38:05.506
AND YOU'RE MAD.

38:05.506 --> 38:06.907
I'M DISAPPOINTED.

38:06.907 --> 38:09.710
BUT YOU KNOW THAT'S NOT ME.

38:09.710 --> 38:11.111
IT IS YOU.

38:11.111 --> 38:12.779
YOU JUST HAVEN'T ACCEPTED IT.

38:12.779 --> 38:14.581
I'M TRYING.

38:14.581 --> 38:17.551
OKAY? CAN'T I GET
SOME CREDIT FOR TRYING?

38:17.551 --> 38:20.954
OKAY. OKAY.

38:20.954 --> 38:22.956
YOU SEE, JUSTIN,

38:22.956 --> 38:27.160
THAT LOOK IN YOUR EYES,
SEE, YOU NEED TO CALM DOWN.

38:27.160 --> 38:29.229
HOW COULD YOU SAY THAT?

38:29.229 --> 38:31.297
BECAUSE YOU'RE GIVING ME
THE SAME LOOK YOU HAD

38:31.297 --> 38:33.867
WHEN YOU ATTACKED ME.
I DIDN'T MEAN TO.

38:33.867 --> 38:36.336
DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND THAT?

38:36.336 --> 38:38.371
YEAH. I DO.

38:38.371 --> 38:42.075
I MEAN, WHEN I SAW
THAT ROOKIE COP SHOOT AT YOU

38:42.075 --> 38:46.146
AND I SAW THE LOOK YOU GAVE ME,
IT BROKE MY HEART.

38:46.146 --> 38:48.381
I WANTED TO GO CRAZY.

38:48.381 --> 38:51.117
I'M TRYING
TO CONTROL MYSELF.

38:51.117 --> 38:53.419
TRYING?

38:53.419 --> 38:58.559
JEFFERY, I'VE NEVER FELT
THESE FEELINGS BEFORE.

38:58.559 --> 39:01.768
OKAY? I'VE ALWAYS THOUGHT
ABOUT THE THINGS

39:01.768 --> 39:03.036
THAT YOU DO TO ME.

39:03.036 --> 39:04.671
I NEVER HAD THEM DONE BEFORE.

39:04.671 --> 39:06.372
I MEAN, I HAVE A WIFE.

39:06.372 --> 39:08.308
I CAN'T BE DOING THAT.

39:08.308 --> 39:11.678
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHO THIS GUY IS.

39:11.678 --> 39:16.850
ALL I KNOW IS THAT I REALLY
LIKE BEING WITH YOU,

39:16.850 --> 39:19.753
AND IT MADE ME
A LITTLE CRAZY,

39:19.753 --> 39:21.487
AND I'M SORRY.

39:21.487 --> 39:23.724
OKAY?

39:23.724 --> 39:26.026
JUSTIN, OKAY.

39:26.026 --> 39:30.864
I ‐‐ LIKE I SAID,
I ACCEPT YOUR APOLOGY.

39:30.864 --> 39:34.234
YEAH, BUT YOU'RE
NOT THE SAME.

39:34.234 --> 39:36.770
WHAT? IT HASN'T EVEN
BEEN THAT LONG.

39:36.770 --> 39:40.173
PLUS, I MEAN, MELISSA IS TRYING
TO KILL HERSELF AND...

39:40.173 --> 39:42.609
MELISSA?
YES, YES, MELISSA,

39:42.609 --> 39:45.145
THE GIRL I'M SUPPOSED TO BE
GETTING MARRIED TO.

39:45.145 --> 39:48.582
MARRY?
YES.

39:48.582 --> 39:50.951
IT'S... YOU DON'T KNOW.
IT'S MY MOTHER. IT'S NOT ME.

39:50.951 --> 39:52.586
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.
YOU'RE GETTING MARRIED?

39:52.586 --> 39:55.121
IT'S A LONG STORY, AND...

39:55.121 --> 39:56.923
WHAT THE HELL IS
GOING ON, JEFFERY?

39:56.923 --> 39:58.892
I ‐‐ IT'S A LONG STORY.
I'LL ‐‐

39:58.892 --> 40:00.426
I'LL TELL YOU
EVERYTHING SOME DAY.

40:00.426 --> 40:02.536
NO, TELL ME NOW.

40:02.536 --> 40:05.205
I DON'T WANT TO TALK
ABOUT IT RIGHT NOW.

40:05.205 --> 40:08.008
JEFFERY. TELL ME.
NO. THIS IS...

40:08.008 --> 40:10.010
YOU REMEMBER WHEN YOU JUST SAID
THAT YOU WERE SORRY?

40:10.010 --> 40:11.244
THIS IS HOW YOU SHOW IT.

40:11.244 --> 40:12.646
HOW?

40:12.646 --> 40:16.482
BY LETTING ME GO AND JUST
LETTING ME LEAVE OUT OF HERE.

40:16.482 --> 40:18.184
YOU NEED TO CALL ME.

40:18.184 --> 40:20.521
I WILL. I'LL CALL YOU.

40:20.521 --> 40:22.255
ARE YOU GOING BACK
TO THE ROOM WITH HIM?

40:24.457 --> 40:26.359
WHAT IF I AM?

40:26.359 --> 40:29.362
I WOULDN'T LIKE IT.

40:29.362 --> 40:31.097
WELL, HE'S MY FRIEND,

40:31.097 --> 40:34.801
AND HE ALWAYS WILL BE,
SO...

40:34.801 --> 40:36.803
DAMN IT.

40:36.803 --> 40:38.038
LOOK.

40:38.038 --> 40:41.041
YOU SAID YOU WERE SORRY,
SO HERE'S YOUR CHANCE.

40:41.041 --> 40:43.544
HERE'S YOUR CHANCE TO SHOW ME
HOW SORRY YOU ARE.

40:43.544 --> 40:45.946
FINE. GO TO HIM.

40:45.946 --> 40:47.280
YOU'RE NOT UPSET?

40:47.280 --> 40:50.216
I'M FINE.

40:50.216 --> 40:51.484
ALL RIGHT.

40:51.484 --> 40:53.620
I'LL CALL YOU LATER.

40:53.620 --> 40:54.821
JEFFERY.

40:54.821 --> 40:57.858
♪♪♪♪

40:59.926 --> 41:03.003
LET ME GO, MAN.

41:03.003 --> 41:04.605
OKAY.

41:07.674 --> 41:10.711
♪♪♪♪

41:12.946 --> 41:14.515
[ SIGHS ]

41:17.250 --> 41:20.286
♪♪♪♪

41:25.358 --> 41:27.628
SO YOU'RE MARRIED.

41:27.628 --> 41:29.796
<i>NEXT, ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:29.796 --> 41:31.397
JEFFERY,
HAVE YOU SEEN WYATT?

41:31.397 --> 41:32.498
I DON'T THINK
HE SHOULD SEE YOU.

41:32.498 --> 41:34.668
‐WHAT?
‐ARE YOU MARRIED?

41:34.668 --> 41:35.702
YES, I AM.

41:35.702 --> 41:37.971
DOES SHE KNOW ABOUT YOU

41:37.971 --> 41:40.473
AND YOUR UNNATURAL
AFFECTIONS?

41:40.473 --> 41:41.875
‐WELL, HE CAN.
‐WHO THE HELL IS THIS?

41:41.875 --> 41:43.777
‐WHAT DO YOU WANT?
‐YOUR DNA.

41:43.777 --> 41:45.411
I WAS TOLD YOU
HAD SOMETHING TO DO

41:45.411 --> 41:47.280
WITH QUINCY'S MURDER.

41:47.280 --> 41:49.215
DAD, HE'S A HORRIBLE PERSON.

41:49.215 --> 41:50.617
WHAT HAPPENED?

41:50.617 --> 41:54.921
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHO OR WHAT I AM.

41:54.921 --> 41:56.657
VINCENT.

41:56.657 --> 41:57.958
WHO'S VINCENT?
